Kimi: "the v0.6.4 gate transcripts show `python3 proofs/bridge_check.py` but do
not include the eval/wave/byte bridges or Lean compilation … the TCB claim is
unaudited in provided evidence." Correct about the *briefing*. `or_review.py`'s
